<plot>On this movie set, the cast and crew treat the background players (a.k.a. atmosphere, extras, props that eat) abysmally. Jane Walter, and a member of the under-class of extras, won't stand for this treatment. She incites a rebellion. The background performers stand up for their rights, and they voice their demands. They don't get everything they want, but they do get their own canvas chairs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?542200</url></doc>
